# Serverless Claw - Environment Setup
#
# Note: This project uses SST v3 (Ion) Secret Management. 
# Do NOT create a .env file for secrets. Instead, use the commands below.

# 1. Telegram Bot Token (from @BotFather)
# npx sst secret set TelegramBotToken <your-token>

# 2. OpenAI API Key
# npx sst secret set OpenAIApiKey <your-api-key>

# 3. GitHub Personal Access Token (for self-improvement loop)
# npx sst secret set GitHubToken <your-github-token>

# --- Optional Local Development Settings ---
# AWS_PROFILE=default
# SST_STAGE=dev

# --- Optional Custom Domain Settings ---
# Note: Ensure you have the domain registered in Route 53 or provide your own certificate configuration if needed.
# CLAW_DOMAIN_API=api.yourdomain.com
# CLAW_DOMAIN_DASHBOARD=claw.yourdomain.com
